						<summary>

						<p>Two fragments of a slab lying near the foot-path, east of the village.</p>						

						<p>Fragmentary. It seems to refer to an enquiry into the revenue taxation during the time of Sultān Bahadaru Moga[lāyi][vāru]. In late characters.</p>						

